&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Quant Virtual Trading Challenge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;About Akuna:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Akuna Capital is an innovative trading firm with a strong focus on collaboration,&amp;nbsp;cutting-edge&amp;nbsp;technology, data driven&amp;nbsp;solutions&amp;nbsp;and automation. We specialize in providing liquidity as an options market-maker – meaning we are committed to providing competitive quotes that we are willing to both buy and sell. To do this successfully, we design and implement our own low latency technologies, trading&amp;nbsp;strategies&amp;nbsp;and mathematical models.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Our Founding Partners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;first conceptualized Akuna in their hometown of Sydney. They opened the firm’s first office in 2011 in the heart of the derivatives industry and the options capital of the world – Chicago. Today, Akuna is proud to&amp;nbsp;operate&amp;nbsp;from&amp;nbsp;additional&amp;nbsp;offices in Sydney, Shanghai, London, and Singapore.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;What&amp;nbsp;you’ll&amp;nbsp;do as a Virtual Quant Trading Challenge Participant:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Are you quantitative, competitive, proficient with Python and looking to test your skills in a Quantitative Trading environment? Break into the Trading industry by participating in our latest simulation! Candidates will gain hands-on trading experience by writing their own market-making bots which will compete both against our models and one another on a simulated exchange. The most profitable submissions will win Akuna swag and expedited recruitment processes in our Quant full-time and internship roles in Chicago!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The challenge will take about 5-8 hours to complete, and the competition will be open for 1 week (from August&amp;nbsp;17&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-fontsize=&quot;12&quot;&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;– August 21st).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Qualities that make great candidates:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;1&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Able to dedicate 5-8 hours uninterrupted to complete the challenge from August&amp;nbsp;17th&amp;nbsp;through August&amp;nbsp;21&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-co

&lt;p&gt;Join &lt;strong&gt;Flowing Water&lt;/strong&gt; for first access to new opportunities, events, and company updates rooted in our culture of knowledge sharing. Communications will be limited, and we will keep your resume on file for roles aligned with your experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our name is inspired by the Australian Aboriginal word meaning “flowing water,” and that spirit runs through everything we do: we are the new wave of rapid innovators with an open flow of communication and knowledge sharing throughout our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We look forward to connecting with you!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;About Akuna:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:200,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Akuna Capital is an innovative trading firm with a strong focus on collaboration, cutting-edge technology, data driven solutions, and automation. We specialize in providing liquidity as an options market maker – meaning we are committed to providing competitive quotes that we are willing to both buy and sell. To do this successfully, we design and implement our own low latency technologies, trading strategies, and mathematical models.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:300,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:350}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Our Founding Partners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;first conceptualized Akuna in their hometown of Sydney. They opened the firm’s first office in 2011 in the heart of the derivatives industry and the options capital of the world – Chicago. &lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Today, Akuna is proud to operate from additional offices in Sydney, Shanghai, London and Singapore.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do as a Broker Trader at Akuna: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Broker Trader to join our growing team at Akuna Capital. The ideal candidate will be a highly motivated individual interested in supporting our team expand coverage and compete in the marketplace. Candidates must possess working relationships inside of and strong familiarity with the options space.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a part of Akuna’s team, you will make markets on options for brokers and banks through chat and voice platforms. Whether making a ‘first show’ market for an inter-dealer broker or executing against an order on the trading floor, the opportunities you identify in the marketplace will be immediately represented in the team’s P&amp;amp;L. You will be entrenched in a collaborative and comprehensive team environment where you will have the opportunity to learn our systems and trading style from some of our most experienced traders. Your previous experience will be expected to provide value from day one even as you adapt to your new role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualities that make great candidates:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of options market making experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial self-starter ready to work in a fast paced, team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong mathematical aptitude giving the ability to maximize trading opportunities in a high-pressure environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective and efficient communication and superior interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capable of developing and maintaining strong working business relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work alongside and communicate with screen traders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for problem-solving and finding creative solutions in an ever-changing market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;VBA or Python programming skills are a plus, but not required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Existing business relationships with inter-dealer, floor or direct counterparty brokers and paper flow&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to react quickly and accurately to rapidly changing market conditions, including the ability to quickly and accurately respond and/or solve math and coding problems are essential functions of the role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

